<P>If I could get Freeport Militia faction in EC, I'd do them as often as I could.&nbsp; I have a (minor) problem with my live frog faction too, but that's nothing that an hour or two of killing undead frogs wouldn't fix.&nbsp; FM, on the other hand, is a royal pain to fix.</P>
